Lonmin to Halt Marikana Platinum Output For One Day After Death of Worker

-- B y   A l a s t a i r   R e e d
-- 
2011-03-29T13:21:09Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-29/lonmin-to-halt-marikana-platinum-output-for-one-day-after-death-of-worker.html
Lonmin Plc (LMI)  said it will cease
production at its Marikana operation in  South Africa  for one day
tomorrow after the death of a worker in an accident.  Lonmin commented in an e-mailed statement today.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Alastair Reed at 
 areed12@bloomberg.net  